text: Telemark is a county in Norway. Skien is the main city in Telemark. Retrieved 2024-08-21 ==History== On 1 January, 2020 the county merged with Vestfold to the county of Vestfold og Telemark. On 1 January, 2024, they split apart again. ==References==
